Liverpool midfielder Lucas Leiva is relishing the prospect of a long-awaited Wembley appearance after injury robbed him .
The Reds made three trips to the national stadium in 2012 after winning the League Cup and losing the FA Cup to Chelsea , but having played his part in the 1-0 quarter-final win at Blackburn .
Lucas is hoping to get his first game at Wembley in the semi-final .